## 5️⃣ UI 컴포넌트 명명

### 🎨 UI 컴포넌트 필수 규칙

> 중요: 모든 UI 변수는 반드시 타입을 접미사로 포함해야 합니다!
> 

### 📊 UI 컴포넌트 명명표

| UI 타입 | 접미사 | 변수명 예시 |
| --- | --- | --- |
| **Button** | `Button` | `_startButton`, `_exitButton` |
| **Text (Legacy)** | `Text` | `_scoreText`, `_timerText` |
| **TextMeshPro** | `TMP` | `_titleTMP`, `_healthTMP` |
| **Image** | `Image` | `_iconImage`, `_healthBarImage` |
| **Slider** | `Slider` | `_volumeSlider`, `_healthSlider` |
| **Toggle** | `Toggle` | `_muteToggle`, `_fullscreenToggle` |
| **InputField** | `InputField` | `_nameInputField` |
| **TMP_InputField** | `InputTMP` | `_chatInputTMP` |
| **Dropdown** | `Dropdown` | `_qualityDropdown` |
| **TMP_Dropdown** | `DropdownTMP` | `_resolutionDropdownTMP` |
| **ScrollRect** | `ScrollRect` | `_inventoryScrollRect` |
| **Panel (GameObject)** | `Panel` | `_mainMenuPanel`, `_settingsPanel` |
| **CanvasGroup** | `CanvasGroup` | `_fadeCanvasGroup` |

### 💻 실전 UI 코드 예시

```csharp
public class MainMenuUI : MonoBehaviour
{
    [Header("Buttons")]
    [SerializeField] private Button _startButton;
    [SerializeField] private Button _settingsButton;
    [SerializeField] private Button _exitButton;

    [Header("Text")]
    [SerializeField] private TextMeshProUGUI _titleTMP;
    [SerializeField] private TextMeshProUGUI _versionTMP;

    [Header("Panels")]
    [SerializeField] private GameObject _mainMenuPanel;
    [SerializeField] private GameObject _settingsPanel;

    // 버튼 이벤트 핸들러
    private void OnStartButtonClicked() { }
    private void OnSettingsButtonClicked() { }
    private void OnExitButtonClicked() { }
}

```

### 🎯 GameHUD 예시

```csharp
public class GameHUD : MonoBehaviour
{
    [Header("Health")]
    [SerializeField] private Image _healthBarFillImage;
    [SerializeField] private TextMeshProUGUI _healthValueTMP;

    [Header("Mana")]
    [SerializeField] private Image _manaBarFillImage;
    [SerializeField] private TextMeshProUGUI _manaValueTMP;

    [Header("Score")]
    [SerializeField] private TextMeshProUGUI _scoreTMP;
    [SerializeField] private TextMeshProUGUI _highScoreTMP;

    [Header("Weapon")]
    [SerializeField] private Image _weaponIconImage;
    [SerializeField] private TextMeshProUGUI _ammoCountTMP;

    public void UpdateHealthBar(float current, float max)
    {
        _healthBarFillImage.fillAmount = current / max;
        _healthValueTMP.text = $"{current:F0}/{max:F0}";
    }

    public void UpdateScore(int score)
    {
        _scoreTMP.text = $"Score: {score:N0}";
    }
}

```

### 🎪 InventoryUI 예시

```csharp
public class InventoryUI : MonoBehaviour
{
    [Header("Panels")]
    [SerializeField] private GameObject _inventoryPanel;
    [SerializeField] private GameObject _itemDetailsPanel;

    [Header("Slots")]
