## 7️⃣ Enum 명명

### 📝 Enum 기본 규칙

> 단수형 사용 (Flags 제외)
> 

```csharp
// ✅ 단수형
public enum GameState
{
    MainMenu,
    Playing,
    Paused,
    GameOver
}

public enum WeaponType
{
    None,
    Pistol,
    Rifle,
    Shotgun
}

public enum Direction
{
    North,
    South,
    East,
    West
}

```

### 🚩 Flags Enum

> 복수형 사용
> 

```csharp
[Flags]
public enum PlayerStates
{
    None = 0,
    Idle = 1,
    Running = 2,
    Jumping = 4,
    Attacking = 8,
    Defending = 16
}

// 사용 예시
PlayerStates state = PlayerStates.Running | PlayerStates.Jumping;

```

### 🎨 UI 관련 Enum

```csharp
public enum UIState
{
    Hidden,
    Showing,
    Visible,
    Hiding
}

public enum PopupType
{
    Info,
    Warning,
    Error,
    Confirmation,
    Reward
}

public enum AnchorPosition
{
    TopLeft,
    TopCenter,
    TopRight,
    Center,
    BottomLeft,
    BottomCenter,
    BottomRight
}

```

